Key features included:

Responsive Design: Uses Tailwind CSS for mobile-first responsive layout

Interactive Map: Leaflet.js integration with dynamic updates

Real-time Validation: IP format validation for both IPv4 and IPv6

Security Checks: VPN/Proxy detection (requires API key for ipqualityscore)

Clipboard Support: Easy copy-to-clipboard functionality

Error Handling: Clear error messages with timeout

Loading States: Visual spinner during API requests

Privacy Section: Collapsible educational content

Auto-detection: Shows user's current IP on initial load

To use this application:

Replace YOUR_API_KEY in the VPN check with a valid IPQualityScore API key

Host on a HTTPS server for security

Optional: Add rate limiting and additional error handling for production

The application provides a clean, modern interface with all requested functionality while maintaining performance and security considerations.
